00:00:00.179 --> 00:00:03.870
Huawei Announces New P8 And P8 Max

00:00:03.870 --> 00:00:08.710
The Chinese electronics manufacturer launched
two new devices at an event at London's Old

00:00:08.710 --> 00:00:09.710
Billingsgate.

00:00:09.710 --> 00:00:16.870
Huawei has launched the Huawei P8 and Huawei
P8 Max at an event at London's Old Billingsgate.

00:00:16.870 --> 00:00:21.880
The P8 smartphone sees the Chinese electronics
maker emphasising design in order to pitch

00:00:21.880 --> 00:00:24.470
for the high-end market.

00:00:24.470 --> 00:00:31.400
The 4G-enabled smartphone is 6.4 mm thick,
with dual SIM cards, with connection to network

00:00:31.400 --> 00:00:35.800
roaming services three time faster than average
phone models.

00:00:35.800 --> 00:00:42.030
The Kirin 930 64-bit Octa-Core chipset claims
to boost performance by around 20 percent

00:00:42.030 --> 00:00:45.600
compared to other phones with similar battery
life.

00:00:45.600 --> 00:00:52.540
Running Android 5.0, it contains 3GB of RAM
and 16 GB of ROM.

00:00:52.540 --> 00:00:57.040
Other features include the ability to remotely
unlock the P8 when connected with a Bluetooth

00:00:57.040 --> 00:01:02.070
device such as the Huawei TalkBand B2 and
an optional E-ink screen on the back of the

00:01:02.070 --> 00:01:03.070
phone.

00:01:03.070 --> 00:01:08.170
"The Huawei P8 design is deeply rooted in
literary tradition, combining elements of

00:01:08.170 --> 00:01:13.600
ancient manuscripts, illuminated books and
the essence of sunlight in stained glass library

00:01:13.600 --> 00:01:16.550
windows," a statement from the company read.

00:01:16.550 --> 00:01:21.570
"It is inspired by the best of human design
from different cultures across the centuries

00:01:21.570 --> 00:01:26.650
and embodies the human spirit of exploration
and beauty," it added.

00:01:26.650 --> 00:01:33.420
Paralleling the iPhone 6 and iPhone 6 Plus,
the Huawei P8max uses the P8 design but features

00:01:33.420 --> 00:01:40.110
a larger 6.8-inch screen, longer battery life
and a camera with light tracing for any environment.

00:01:40.110 --> 00:01:46.470
"The goal of Huawei P8 is to become the most
user-friendly smartphone for consumers globally,"

00:01:46.470 --> 00:01:50.750
said Richard Yu, CEO of Huawei Consumer Business
Group.

00:01:50.750 --> 00:01:55.939
"Through in-depth market research, Huawei
has addressed the most pressing pain points

00:01:55.939 --> 00:01:58.079
for premium smartphone users today."

00:01:58.079 --> 00:02:04.659
"Huawei seamlessly combines the best elements
of style and durability in this device, delivering

00:02:04.659 --> 00:02:10.539
a revolutionary user experience - especially
in terms of camera capabilities and network

00:02:10.539 --> 00:02:11.900
connectivity.

00:02:11.900 --> 00:02:17.419
He added: "Building on the outstanding market
performance of Huawei's P series, we fully

00:02:17.419 --> 00:02:22.439
believe the Huawei P8 will become one of the
most popular smartphones of 2015."

